Impyisi Irwaye

Kera, kera cyane, hari igihe cyinzara ikomeye. Impyisi ifite ubwenge cyane yigize nkaho irwaye kuburyo itashobora no gusohoka munzu.

Inyamaswa nyinshi zagiye kuyisura kuyihumuriza. Ariko nta n'imwe muri zo zigeze zisohoka!

Umunsi umwe nyuma ya saa sita, urukwavu rwifuja gusura impyisi.

Rwagiye mu buvumo bw'impyisi. Ariko mu buryo butunguranye,rurahagarara, rubona hari inyamaswa nyinsi zinjira, kandi nta zisohoka.

Rwagumye hanze rurangurura ijwi riti: "Uraho neza? Ufite ubuzima bwiza, nshuti yanjye magara? Uratera imbere?"

Impyisi irasubiza iti: "Ntugire ubwoba, nshuti yanjye. Injira unyisujyeho nshuti nziza!"


"Yoo, sinzi neza niba ngomba kwinjira. Mu byukuri, nta mwanya mfite ubu, kandi ufite abashyitsi benshi."

"Oya, oya, urukwavu, ibintu byose ni byiza. Nta muntu uhari hano. Ntabwo ari byiza ko nguma aho ndwaye kandi ndinjyenyine."

"Urabeshya! Ndikubona  ibirenge by'inyamaswa zinjiye ariko zitarasohoka ..."

Impyisi yaracecetse maze urukwavu ruti: "Urabeho, nshuti yanjye, ndumva nzagusura undi munsi."

Urukwavu rwirukira kure yaho hantu!
